        </p>
        <h2>Why Choose EasyBus?</h2>
        <p>
            We understand that travel planning can be time-consuming and stressful. That's why we have created EasyBus to offer a seamless experience from booking to boarding. With EasyBus, you get access to a wide range of bus operators, route options, and the convenience of booking from anywhere at any time.
        </p>
