                <li><strong>Secure Payments:</strong> Safe and secure payment options for a worry-free booking experience.</li>
                <li><strong>24/7 Customer Support:</strong> Get assistance any time you need it, with our dedicated support team.</li>
                <li><strong>Real-Time Tracking:</strong> Stay updated on your bus location and arrival times with our live tracking feature.</li>
                <li><strong>Discounts and Offers:</strong> Enjoy exclusive deals and discounts on your favorite routes.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p>
